OL,3,CBlackpool appoint former Manchester
OL,4,CUnited defender Steve Bruce as head
OL,5,Ccoach
OL,7,FBlackpool Football Club have appointed
OL,8,Fformer Manchester United defender
OL,9,FSteve Bruce as their new head coach.
OL,11,FThe club sit 22nd in League One having
OL,12,Fnot won a single league game. They
OL,13,Fhave lost two and drawn two leaving
OL,14,Fthem with on two points on the board.
OL,16,FThe Tangerines sacked Neil Critchley
OL,17,Fin August after starting their
OL,18,Fcampaign with back-to-back defeats.
