OL,3,CBlackpool appoint former Manchester
OL,4,CUnited defender Steve Bruce as head
OL,5,Ccoach
OL,7,FThe 63-year-old who has managed a
OL,8,Fnumber of clubs including Aston Villa,
OL,9,FWigan Athletic, Newcastle United, Hull
OL,10,FCity and West Bromwich Albion - which
OL,11,Fwas his last job in October 2022.
OL,13,FBruce has signed a two-year deal with
OL,14,FBlackpool, which will see his long-
OL,15,Fterm assistant Steve Agnew will join
OL,16,Fhim at Bloomfield Road, along with
OL,17,Fcoaches Richard Keogh, Stephen Dobbie
OL,18,Fand Steve Banks.
