OL,3,CBlackpool appoint former Manchester
OL,4,CUnited defender Steve Bruce as head
OL,5,Ccoach
OL,7,FIn an interview with the club, Steve
OL,8,FBruce said: "I'm delighted to be back
OL,9,Fin football and to take charge of this
OL,10,Ffantastic football club.
OL,12,F"I'd like to thank Simon, Julian and
OL,13,FDavid for giving me this great
OL,14,Fopportunity. I look forward to meeting
OL,15,Fall of the staff and players in the
OL,16,Fcoming days as we prepare for what we
OL,17,Fall hope will be an exciting season at
OL,18,FBloomfield Road."
