OL,7,FBlackpool's owner Simon Sadler said:
OL,8,F"I'm confident that Steve's experience
OL,9,Fand leadership qualities will be a
OL,10,Ftremendous asset for Blackpool
OL,11,FFootball Club.
OL,13,F"His organised approach coupled with
OL,14,Fhis desire to build a hardworking and
OL,15,Fentertaining side is a large part of
OL,16,Fwhat attracted us to him.
OL,18,F"Additionally, Steve's ability to help
OL,19,Fgrow and develop not only our playing
OL,20,Fstaff but also our coaching talent was
OL,21,Fimportant to us.
