OL,7,F"Alongside his assistant Steve Agnew,
OL,8,Fthere is a great opportunity for two
OL,9,Fof our former-players at the early
OL,10,Fstages of their coaching careers to
OL,11,Flearn from a duo who possess
OL,12,Funrivalled qualities.
OL,14,F"We hope that this blend will get the
OL,15,Fvery best out of our talented squad."
